# Document Converter

<p align="center">
  <img src="assets/icon.ico" alt="Document Converter Logo" width="128">
</p>

<p align="center">
  <strong>A comprehensive Python library for document conversion with batch processing, intelligent caching, and template rendering.</strong>
</p>

